Explain what localization is:

Android is found in a thousand different platforms in every corner of the world. 
To ensure, that the application, that you are making, reaches the most audience, 
you will want to enable localization. Localization handles all your media including, audio, text, currency, numbers,
and converts it to the native language, that you are currently residing in. 


